{"tid":855443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傑哥為小麗企街　伯伯眼濕濕","createTime":"2018-10-10T05:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T07:05:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b382f20aa9a8424ed5f0d0e0e951bad00d95e7","tid":855443,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181010/20518873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F20518873&d=VvRda%2FphPWYygqpmMXAMCZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c96a9639\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F20518873&h=986b64ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181010/20518873</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月10日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：傑哥為小麗企街　伯伯眼濕濕 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181010/large/a1505a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181010%2Flarge%2Fa1505a.gif&h=2f7da192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉小麗喺佐敦開街站做宣傳，公民黨主席梁家傑亦有到場協助。梁家傑fb圖片<br />\n <br />\n首日報名至今一星期，劉小麗能否過關避過「二度DQ」，至今仍然懸疑未決；雖然生死未卜，劉小麗依舊做好準備，朝朝落區開街站，今朝更獲曾經選過特首，知道「有得揀，先至係老闆」嘅公民黨主席梁家傑協助，喺佐敦開站做宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n傑哥喺facebook話，今早有位伯伯同佢握手並指：「見到你我就有希望」，說時還激動得眼有淚光，佢就向伯伯講啦：「我得一個人作用有限，香港係因為有好多哥哥你咁樣對香港不離不棄、唔趨炎附勢、唔忘本、堅持香港嘅核心價值同制度，唔做破壞香港幫兇嘅人，先至係香港有希望嘅理由。」<br />\n<br />\n傑哥強調若每個有心嘅港人都做自己可以做嘅事，大家同心協力，香港一定可以捱過去、撐得住，呼籲選民11.25九西補選撐民主派唯一嘅候選人一票。  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：欣‧為你建制同鄉被眾籌　多多益善最少$10 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：堂叔你好嘢！張堅庭同張達明有親 (李八方)"},{"pid":"af8ac8ba1106e31d0f1d373be3f05957d0a80c7f","tid":855443,"uid":43116,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:02:36.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"a55369dc0114010dc3b2bd3a0a336fb9cd963ce0","tid":855443,"uid":93074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9942c69e364ff60cb3b6caad883b3c4ec7aa50d0","tid":855443,"uid":64874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a55369dc0114010dc3b2bd3a0a336fb9cd963ce0","tid":855443,"uid":93074,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"借07年袋巾&ldquo;選特首&rdquo;個時個七十歲阿伯希望香港有民主條橋，呢啲花招呃唔到後生仔"},{"pid":"ce8f16620c967d8ff829dcef6ab1728b57bfd38a","tid":855443,"uid":169529,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"兩舊都係屎入去張票寫個屌字算"},{"pid":"f8de487867aa6ddf4b78d35a0d16a7325142c83b","tid":855443,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:51:43.000Z","msg":"爭取普選爭到唔見影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fc5aebf393e9b22e2fa0603c3c8dea95c9b1c1","tid":855443,"uid":34223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"收撚皮喇毒果 個標題睇到都打冷震呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e03bbcb09547dadbc68dfda5a8502b85f532c9","tid":855443,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"人地去美國指責美國制裁中國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話美國應該回歸理性談判，唔應該用貿易手段呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死撚開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd3074dd622dfafa81948ca0a779d1a98623e75","tid":855443,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:52:16.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />